- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses Machine Learning techniques to improve robot performance. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve visual perception for the robot to navigate the environment. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with controlling the robot's locomotion.
